      "text": "Neo Labs The lab is the spine of this site: real deployed systems, honest prototypes, and the roadmap between them — built without pretending any of it is further along than it is. A real site feature: browser UI → same-origin /api/chat on Vercel → provider, with server-side keys and a rule-based fallback that never fakes AI. A simulated retrieval layer with visible pipeline states, extraction-intent guardrails, relevance scoring, source-boundary metadata, and a claim-safety label on every result. Problem, architecture, security decisions, QA evidence, lessons, resume bullets, and interview talking points — documented like a release.",
