      "text": "Resume proof Designed refusals, claim-safety labels, empty states, and fallback states before adding any answer-generation layer. Mapped a staged path from local public-content ranking to embeddings, vector index, citations, and evals. Built a keyboard-friendly browser prototype with pipeline state, ranked cards, audit preview, and session metrics. Connects the future RAG path to the same server-side key discipline already used by the site's live /api/chat. Shows public-only indexing, private-data refusal, route whitelisting, no browser secrets, and no persistent query storage. Separates measured session behavior from planned retrieval benchmarks and names the tests needed before production claims.",
