      "text": "Problem A technical portfolio full of demos still leaves a visitor — or a hiring manager, or an admissions reviewer — doing the work of figuring out what is real. The interesting engineering problem was building a search layer that could answer those questions honestly: That framing turned a \"search demo\" into a claim-safety problem — which is exactly the problem real AI products have.",
